{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "The objectives of this course are:1. To help students better understand intercultural workplaces2. To help students communicate effectively in an English-speaking working environment3. To develop students’ language skills (listening, speaking, reading, and writing) with a focus on business contexts4. To develop students’ cross-cultural awareness&nbsp;5. To help students improve their TOEIC test-taking skills", "到達目標": "1. Students will develop their cultural awareness.2. Students will acquire the English communication skills needed in business settings.3. Students will familiarize themselves with English as it is used in business situations.4. Students will become better TOEIC test-takers.", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "<span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:;\">Practical English D (01-02)</span>", "授業の概要・背景": "", "授業方法": "1. This course will be conducted in English only and English will be the means of communication between the students and the instructor.&nbsp;&nbsp;(Students will also be expected to communicate with one another in English.)2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Students are encouraged to actively participate in class discussions, both independently and collaboratively, in order to enhance their competence and confidence in English and also to create a better learning environment for all.&nbsp;", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin:0cm;font-size:medium;font-family:Cambria,serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\">【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;\">Startup Week</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"MS Mincho\";\">】リンク：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",serif;color:rgb(238,0,0);\">https://</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\",seri